---
title: Sprint State Diagram
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created : Sprint created

    Created --> InProgress : Start sprint\n[properties locked]

    InProgress --> Finished : Time is up

    state sprint_type <<choice>>
    Finished --> sprint_type

    sprint_type --> Review : ReviewSprint
    sprint_type --> Releasing : ReleaseSprint\n[pipeline starts]

    Review --> Closed : Close\n[requires review summary]
    Closed --> [*]

    Releasing --> Released : Pipeline success\n[notify SM + PO]
    Releasing --> Cancelled : Pipeline failed\n[notify SM + PO]

    Cancelled --> Releasing : Retry release\n[SM decision]

    Released --> [*]

    note right of Created : Can modify properties\nCan add backlog items
    note right of InProgress : Properties locked\nNo backlog item changes
    note left of Releasing : Pipeline executing\nNo modifications allowed
    note right of Cancelled : SM can retry\nor leave cancelled
